<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <title>CSS Writing Modes Test: vertical align - 'zero length (0em)' (central baseline with vertical layout)</title>
    <link rel="author" title="Hajime Shiozawa" href="mailto:hajime.shiozawa@gmail.com" />
    <link rel="help" title="4.4. Baseline Alignment" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-writing-modes/#baseline-alignment" />
    <meta name="assert" content="This test checks the generation of text baseline with vertical align property. When 'writing-mode' is vertical and when 'text-orientation' is 'mixed', 'upright' or 'use-glyph-orientation', then the central baseline is used as the dominant baseline." />
    <meta name="flags" content="ahem image" />
    <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
      div > p {
        font: 40px/1 "Ahem";
        background-color: orange;
      }

      /* vertical-align */
      img {
        vertical-align: 0em;
      }
      img.box {
        margin-top: -50px;
      }
      img.line {
        margin-top: -210px;
      }

      /* writing-mode property */
      .vertical-rl {
        writing-mode: vertical-rl;
      }

      /* text-orientation property */
      .mixed {
        text-orientation: mixed;
      }
      .upright {
        text-orientation: upright;
      }
      .use-glyph-orientation {
        text-orientation: use-glyph-orientation;
      }

      /* font-size */
      .half {
        vertical-align: text-top;
        font-size: 0.5em;
      }
  ]]></style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Test passes if ...</p>
    <ol>
      <li>if the <strong>left</strong> edge of black strip is touching a thin blue line in each 3 orange rectangles.</li>
      <li>if the <strong>center</strong> of yellow box (showed as a blue line) is aligned to a thin blue line in each 3 orange rectangles.</li>
      <li>if all 3 orange rectangles are <strong>identical</strong>.</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="vertical-rl">
      <p class="mixed"><span><span class="half">LLLLLLLLL</span>
          <img class="line" src="./support/blue-vert-line_1x220.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" />
          <img class="box" src="./support/vert-box_59x59.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></span>
      </p>
      <p class="upright"><span><span class="half">LLLLLLLLL</span>
          <img class="line" src="./support/blue-vert-line_1x220.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" />
          <img class="box" src="./support/vert-box_59x59.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></span>
      </p>
      <p class="use-glyph-orientation"><span class="outer"><span class="half">LLLLLLLLL</span>
          <img class="line" src="./support/blue-vert-line_1x220.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" />
          <img class="box" src="./support/vert-box_59x59.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
